SUMMARY:Live Music and Food Truck
DESCRIPTION:Live Music & Food Truck Night at Great Bear Vineyards in Davis \nFriday\, April 17 | 5–8pmTicket Includes: Glass of Wine & Live Music\nJoin us for a special Friday evening celebrating music\, community\, and local talent at the vineyard! \nWe’re thrilled to feature the Davis Senior High School Jazz Band\, bringing smooth jazz\, energy\, and Blue Devil pride to the vines. Sit back\, relax\, and enjoy an unforgettable live performance in a beautiful\, laid-back setting.\n Buenos Aires Grill will be onsite serving up their delicious empanadas and authentic Argentinian bites—perfectly paired with your included glass of wine and more available by the glass or bottle.\nSip\, savor\, and soak in the sounds of these talented young musicians while supporting the next generation of artists. \n Great music. Delicious food. A chance to give back.The perfect way to spend your Friday night—we hope to see you there!
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/live-music-and-food-truck-26/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards  24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/great-bear-vineyards.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
